{
  "texts": [
    "GAN is the most adopted facial reenactment image generator.",
    "In 2016, Thies et al. [5] developed one of the first tools, namely Face2Face, for facial reenactment.",
    "It was a real-time system that created a 3D face model based on the input image and used its 3D geometry to render the fake face.",
    "Face2Face was one of the first tools of its kind.",
    "Reenactment can also be carried out using purely one video input with the use of a method proposed by [6]."
  ]
}